    ],
    "summary": "On 26 September 2021 at approximately 0930 hours on West Delta 30 T production platform, an Instrumentation & Electrical Tech contracted with W-Industries was removing damaged tubing from a well panel when wind caught the panel door, causing it to swing open and pinch the worker's right index finger between the panel side and door hinge, resulting in a laceration requiring medical treatment beyond first aid.",
